data.description: Welcome to 1705 Chesapeake Drive! This charming updated Cape Cod home has so much to offer with 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms. The floor plan has a great flow and feels open while also allowing privacy. Refinished wood flooring & Brand new carpet. Nice sized bedrooms including primary bedroom with bath on the first floor. Fenced backyard and detached garage just right for family days and entertaining. This home offers the quietness of a tucked away neighborhood, but you'll only be a short drive to everything Chesapeake has to offer. Quick access to the interstates, bases, Shipyards, shopping centers, restaurants, and much more. Book your showing today!
